		"AbilityTooltips"
		{
				"alchemist_acid_spray"	"Acid Spray secures your lane, but also pushes it. It also helps you improve your farming, but at a high-mana cost. Use Acid Spray right before fights to lower their armour to make fighting easier."
				"alchemist_unstable_concoction"	"Unstable Concotion takes 5 seconds to reach its max stun duration. Before TP\'ing into a fight or to defend a teammate, active your Unstable Concotion so you can hit foes at a longer length without them being able to flee or getting into fog of war."
				"alchemist_goblins_greed"	"We get a point in Greevil\'s Greed early on for the multiplier bonus earned by collecting bounty runes; don\'t hesitate to leave the lane for that bounty rune every two minutes as it will hasten your gold collection to an astronomical amount."
				"alchemist_chemical_rage"	"This ultimate has a relatively low cooldown and offers a ton of HP/Mana regeneration. Use it to farm jungle; it\'s also great to survive ganks and get that extra movement speed."
